# Deterministic line endings: Biome's formatter demands LF; without this, Windows
# checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) smudge working copies to CRLF and `verify` goes red
# on format for files whose committed content is fine. eol=lf makes checkout byte-stable.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.jpg binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
